#summary jsCore Clean subroutine.
#labels Phase-Implementation

*syntax:*
{{{
object.Clean
}}}
Remove all contends in jsObject or jsArray.

== Samples ==
{{{
Dim o
Set o = jsArray()

Sub AddUser(name, surname)
        Set o(Null) = jsObject()
        o(Null)("name") = name
        o(Null)("surname") = surname
End Sub

AddUser "tuğrul", "topuz"
AddUser "nasrettin", "hoca"
AddUser "cin", "ali"
o.Flush

o.Clean

AddUser "barış", "manço"
o.Flush
}}}
